review:
Dr. Dimple is absolutely a well knowledgeable, simple, soft spoken, extremely caring and very friendly person. 
She treated my Son ( Maxillofacial Surgery) and did a thorough post-surgery follow-ups. 
She is one of her kind who is very rare to see in this fast moving materialistic word / life. With actual treatments, through her kindness and polite words, she heals many pains and built confidence. 
She has a healing hand and her diagnosis is always phenomenal.
I strongly recommend Dr. Dimple, bcoz, more than a Doctor( her profession), she is an amazing human being whom you can entrust forever.

I am happy and satisfied with Dr.Dimple's diagnosis & suggested procedure. She has a lot of patience in explaining the diagnosis and intended procedure.
She does her job well and keeps patients informed about what's happening while the surgery is being done. Overall she supported me well throughout my  treatment.

She is an amazing human being and with her medical skill set, she becomes best at her job. My father was diagnosed with squamous cell carcinoma, a skin cancer in mouth. She takes personal care of her patients, always approachable, soft spoken and great with her treatment. Highly  recommended.

We consulted Dr. Dimple for my son when she was with Bhagwan Mahaveer Jain Hospital. A cyst was getting formed around my Son‚Äôs teeth which was still inside the jaw bone. It required surgery to be removed. She very well handled my son‚Äôs queries & helped him calm down his anxiety on the day of surgery. She also helped us in completing all paper work pre and post surgery. I would definitely recommend her.

I have been a patient of Dr. Dimple for my jaw treatment for a while now. The first time i visited her for consultation, I felt the positivity while she was diagnosing. The tests recommended by her were apt. She did a great job in treating my pain and currently undergoing treatment for permanent cure. Must say, it has helped me a lot. Recovery has been fantastic. Thank you doctor.
I am happy to share my experience during my treatment ,Your Treatment is Excellence, Hence i am Getting  speedy Recovery ,

Dr.Dimple is an amazing doctor with exceptional ability to connect to their patients. She was extremely nice and explained my condition in a clear manner. In addition to being an amazing doctor, she also has excellent communication skills which makes my every visit exciting.
Overall, I had a great experience as a first timer. Highly recommended.

I am very scared of any surgical procedures, okay.  That is the first thing i want to tell you. 
Secondly the thing you all should know is that_ Dr Dimple Sethia is one of the kind doctor who changed my entire experience. She has the skills and the way procedures executed are exceptional. I have been treated by the best doctor! 
I would definitely recommend to all viewers / reader to approach. You can also be the lucky patient, you know! :) 

Thank You.
